data.description: Your search in Windsong Ranch is over- Welcome to *Dude Perfect Paradise*. The best location and floor plan in Windsong Ranch, and former home of a Dude Perfect dude, is now available to make your own! Prime location steps away from the clubhouse and amenities. This gem boasts 2 separate garages with plenty of storage space. If the large primary bedroom, bathroom, and walk-in closet aren't enough, don't fret- there is a SECOND downstairs bedroom with in-suite bathroom perfect for guests or traveling family. The open kitchen with large granite island and built-in gas range will help make those holiday meals come together with ease. Upstairs, find two additional bedrooms and another two rooms ideal for storage, reading, or working. Immerse in entertainment with a theater fully equipped and furnished for the new owner. Stay cool on the covered rear patio, perfect for kicking back in spring and summer. Enjoy tennis matches from the spacious front porch. Pound It, Noggin! See Ya!
